---
By: Tai-Shang
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 199
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Golden Rule
---
Pity the misfortunes of others; rejoice in the well-being of others; help
those who are in want; save men in danger; rejoice at the success of
others; and sympathize with their reverses, even as though you were in
their place.
